I"7<h2 id="create-blog-using-jekyll">Create Blog Using Jekyll</h2>

<h4 id="0-install-ruby">0. Install Ruby</h4>

<p>Download Link: https://rubyinstaller.org/downloads/</p>

<p>Test: Open gitbash</p>
<div class="language-javascript highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nx">$</span> <span class="nx">ruby</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="nx">v</span>
<span class="c1">//should output a ruby version</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<h4 id="1-install-rubygems">1. Install RubyGems</h4>

<p>Download Link: https://rubygems.org/</p>

<div class="language-javascript highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nx">$cd</span> <span class="nx">D</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="err">\</span><span class="nx">Software</span><span class="err">\</span><span class="nx">rubygems</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mf">2.7</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="c1">//download path</span>
<span class="nx">$ruby</span> <span class="nx">setup</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">rb</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<h4 id="2-install-jekyll">2. Install jekyll</h4>

<div class="language-javascript highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nx">$gem</span> <span class="nx">install</span> <span class="nx">jekyll</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<h4 id="3-create-a-jekyll-demo">3. Create a jekyll demo</h4>

<div class="language-javascript highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nx">$cd</span> <span class="o">/</span><span class="nx">firstdemo</span> <span class="c1">//empty folder</span>
<span class="nx">$jekyll</span> <span class="k">new</span> <span class="nx">testblog</span>
<span class="nx">$cd</span> <span class="nx">testblog</span>
<span class="nx">$jekyll</span> <span class="nx">server</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>Open you browser and go to http://127.0.0.1:4000/ to see the blog demo</p>

